    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just... i've always been the one helping them. being the strong one. now it's reversed and it feels so wrong. they spend their whole weekends helping me move around or getting me to doctor appointments and i just see them looking at their watches or sighing. i don't want to be a project for them to finish. i'd rather just be gone than be another thing they have to worry about.",
