      "content": "i know people say things will get better but it's just the truth of it.. i'm just an obstacle in their lives now. it would be so much kinder if i could just step aside and let them live their own lives without having to look after an old woman. wouldn't it be more peaceful for everyone if i just... stopped being a problem?",
